Domain-Driven Design Structure:

Code
apps/web/
â”œâ”€â”€ domains/                       # Business domains
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ user/                      # User domain
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ components/           # Domain components
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ composables/          # Domain logic
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ pages/               # Domain pages
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ stores/              # Domain state
â”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ types/               # Domain types
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ product/                   # Product domain
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ components/
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ composables/
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ pages/
â”‚   â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ stores/
â”‚   â”‚   â””â”€â”€ types/
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ order/                     # Order domain
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ components/
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ composables/
â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ pages/
